data.description: Well Maintained; 4 Bedroom 2 Bath Home located on a dead end street on S 15th Ave. The fourth Bedroom in the basement is non-conforming. House includes an Office and a Large room upstairs. Spacious living room! You will enjoy the large fully fenced backyard for those Family Gatherings in the Summer Time! Their is also a one car detached garage with some additional storage in the back! Also a very Nice Cherry Fruit tree available on the property! Please call of text the Listing Agent ; Mariana Cuevas at (509)930-5882
